      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments use the same pump geometry, fluid, and operating range as the intended COU; any gaps between validation scenario and COU are documented.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry identical to the COU device. Blood analog fluid properties match clinical CPB conditions. Operating points span the intended clinical flow-speed envelope. The validation scenario is judged highly representative of the COU."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
