      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2, full numerical solver error quantification beyond residual monitoring is not required. Residuals for continuity, momentum, and turbulence quantities converge to below 1e-5 for all runs, confirming adequate iterative convergence. Detailed round-off and iterative error decomposition is scoped to higher MRL assessments."
