      "rationale": "The k-omega SST turbulence model and Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model are documented as the selected model forms. Justification for these selections references published literature on blood pump CFD. Full model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2 and is deferred."
    },
